<plot>When parents Charlotte and Jens take to Christianity in search of new identity their daughters Line and Pernille conceive it as a major crisis. Their parents, who used to be admired by all the girls' friends, are now a laughing stock. When a letter arrives with an invitation for the parents to join a gospel choir, the girls plan a plot to let the family return to their unreligious lives.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?227775</url></doc>
